The bank where Lic. Petra works, now has a new system to review the history, and allows you to identify the data for a credit prospect.

In the new system, now you just have to enter the age of the prospect, its years worked and its current income and now the algorithm will work as follows.

If the age is greater than 18, the years greater than 5 and the income greater than $ 5,000.00, must show a message that is your credit will be in the range of $ 10,000 to $ 15,000.

On the other hand, if the age is greater than 35, the years older than 10 years and the income greater than $ 10,000, must show a message that the credit range will be $ 25,000 to $ 30,000.

If the age is greater than 60, the years greater than 20 and the income greater than $ 20,000, must show a message that the credit range will be $ 50,000 to $ 100,000.

If any of the age ranges, years of work ranges or income ranges does not coincide, you should simply show a message that needs to contact an advisor.

Algoritmo sin_titulo
	Escribir "Ingresa tu edad"
	Leer edad
	Escribir "Ingresa los a침os trabajados"
	Leer At
	Escribir "Ingresa el ingreso actual"
	Leer inact
	
	si edad > 18 y at > 5 y inact > 5000 Entonces
		credito = "Tu credito es de 10,000 a 15,000"
		si edad > 35 y at > 10 y inact > 10000 Entonces
			credito = "Tu credito es de 25,000 a 30,000"
		FinSi
	FinSi
	si edad > 60 y at > 20 y inact > 20000 Entonces
		credito = "Tu credito es de 50,000 a 1000,000" 
	SiNo
		escribir"Contacta a un acesor"
	FinSi
	Mostrar credito 
FinAlgoritmo

